        "text": "## Result\n\n**No stability constants measured in supercritical CO₂ are available in the NIST SRD-46 database.**\n\nThe database contains **79,063** stability-constant measurements, and **100% of them** were measured in water (H₂O) as the solvent. There are no entries for supercritical CO₂ — or any non-aqueous solvent, for that matter.",
